    				Services    			
  			

  			
  			
  			
    			Ramesh has been a very active member of professional communities in which he did research. He served on editorial/advisory boards of numerous magazines and journals. He also served in various capacities at many different conferences and workshops. His role in conferences have been from serving on Program Committees to serving as a General Chair.
The editorial boards he has served on includes:
ACM Transactions on Multimedia Computing, Communications, and ApplicationsComputer Vision Graphics and Image ProcessingIEEE Intelligent Systems MagazineIEEE Multimedia MagazineIEEE Transactions on MultimediaJournal of Optical SocietyMachine Vision and ApplicationsMultimedia SystemsMultimedia Tools and ApplicationsOptical Engineering
The conferences he has been involved with includes:
ACM MultimediaACM Multimedia Information RetrievalIEEE Computer Vision and Pattern RecognitionIEEE International Conference on Computer VisionIEEE International Conference on Data EngineeringIEEE International Conference on Multimedia and ExpoWorkshops on Motion Analysis
    			  			

  			


	
	
			

		
	



	   

	   
	   	
	   
	   
			



